description: Easy to use web server for building web apps that use sql databases generated automatically from c# classes.
releaseNotes:
+ Improve nonZero handling in DataTables.
+ Make sure phone menu icon appears on top.
+ Allow ListForm and DataTable select url to include additional get parameters.
+ Added ContentTypes list to convert file extension to MIME type.
+ Support Charsets and Encodings other that windows-1252 in form posts.
+ Added content-type for .svg files.
+ Admin/EditSettings uses derived Settings type.
+ Factored common code in NamespaceDef.
+ WebServer tries to find derived ErrorModule when displaying exceptions.
+ Edited form templates.
+ Added listform template.
+ Ensure resize is called after all graphics loaded.
+ Fix bug if sClass is set in Form.
+ Ensure all menus are shown if a button is added (and resize after show).
+ Ensure menu3 is shown if a button is added (allowing it to be hidden by default, if required).
+ Save button now does what Save and Close used to do. new apply option adds an Apply button which does what Save used to do (i.e. Save and redisplay).
+ Bug fix to addRow option in ListForm.
title: CodeFirstWebFramework
